      "discrepancies_en": "Some outlets romanize the Home Minister as Sudhan Gurung; English coverage also uses Sudan Gurung. The Himalayan Times spelled the Tourism minister as Khadak Raj Poudel; Radio Nepal used Khadka Raj Paudel—we follow the Radio Nepal spelling for the roster. Radio Nepal summarized several portfolios briefly; secondary ministries (e.g. Water Supply with Health) follow common merged-line reporting and the platform tracker ministry labels.",
